<body>
<p>Reports AspectJ pointcut designators which are not supported by Spring.</p>

<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code lang="xml">
&lt;beans&gt;
  &lt;aop:config &gt;
      &lt;aop:pointcut expression="<strong>@this</strong>(Anno)  &lt;!-- '@this' pointcut designator isn't supported by Spring --&gt;
                  and <strong>adviceexecution</strong>()"/&gt; &lt;!--  'adviceexecution' pointcut designator isn't supported by Spring --&gt;
      &lt;aop:pointcut expression="!@annotation(Anno)"/&gt;
    &lt;/aop:config&gt;
&lt;/beans&gt;
</code></pre>
</body>
</html>
